{
  "texts": [
    "The rating value is R1, meaning that the photo is significant and will require additional time (15 min).",
    "If a photo has a rating value of R2, it has a low priority and can be deleted to make room for another.",
    "The considered three features for each image are fuzzified.",
    "The Fuzzified Arrival Time (FAT), Fuzzified Time to Live (FTTL), and Fuzzified Priority (FP) is used to predict the value of R. They are calculated as shown in Eqs.",
    "(1), (2), and (3). ii."
  ]
}